~ Final gap audit for v0.1.0 freeze

~ GAP TEST 2: unique() builtin
try:
    show unique([1, 2, 1, 3])
caught err:
    show "unique MISSING"

~ GAP TEST 3: sum() builtin
try:
    show sum([1, 2, 3, 4])
caught err:
    show "sum MISSING"

~ GAP TEST 4: count() / frequency
try:
    show count([1, 1, 1, 2], 1)
caught err:
    show "count MISSING"

~ GAP TEST 6: Slicing syntax
try:
    show [1, 2, 3, 4, 5][1..3]
caught err:
    show "Slicing MISSING"

~ GAP TEST 7: Scientific notation in source
try:
    make x = 1e5
caught err:
    show "Scientific notation MISSING"

~ GAP TEST 9: Reverse on strings/text
try:
    show reverse("hello")
caught err:
    show "reverse(text) MISSING"

~ GAP TEST 10: split on empty string works?
show split("hello", "")

